title: Appeals Court Will Not Reinstate Trump’s Revised Travel Ban
url: https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/25/us/politics/trump-travel-ban-blocked.html
quote: The revised order, issued on March 6, “speaks with vague words of national security, but in context drips with religious intolerance, animus and discrimination,” the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit, in Richmond, Va., concluded in its 205-page ruling.
